      {
        "id": "opening01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "opencol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "{{contact.first_name}},",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 28,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text01",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Twelve days into your venue search, and you're probably asking yourself a lot of the same questions that every couple asks at this stage. Let me address what I hear most often — directly and honestly.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FDFCFA",
          "padding": "40px 40px 20px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "faq01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "faqcol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "\"What if we find something better after we book?\"",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text02",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>You might. That's the nature of exploring — you never know what you might find around the next corner.</p><p>But here's what I want you to consider: you've now seen Cameron Estate. You know what we offer, what our spaces look like, what's included in our pricing, and how we work with couples. You've developed clarity on what matters to you by seeing what's actually out there.</p><p>If another venue offers something significantly different — a feature you genuinely need that we don't have, a date we don't have available, a price point that works better for your budget — then you'll know. And you can make an informed decision. But that clarity only comes from seeing what's actually out there, which you're doing.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 10px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "image01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "imgcol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "img01",
                "values": {
                  "src": {
                    "url": "https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/G7APqyfJ6lyi4l28noZj/media/6989327a0a7fd1ecad41c546.jpg",
                    "width": 600,
                    "autoWidth": true
                  },
                  "alt": "Cameron Estate Inn Exterior",
                  "width": 520,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "0 40px 30px 40px",
                  "borderRadius": 6
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "0 0 0 0"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "faq02",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "faqcol02",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head03",
                "values": {
                  "text": "\"Is the pricing really final? Are there hidden fees?\"",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text03",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Yes. Your proposal includes exactly what we discussed — your all-inclusive price for your estimated guest count, covers all food, beverage, venue access, rentals, and coordination services. No surprises. No hidden fees. No add-ons that you didn't expect showing up three months before your wedding.</p><p>If your guest count changes significantly, we'll adjust accordingly. But there are no secret \"service fees,\" no \"admin charges,\" no \"setup costs\" that appear later.</p><p>The number we quote is the number you pay.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#F5F1EB",
          "padding": "30px 40px 10px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "image02",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "imgcol02",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "img02",
                "values": {
                  "src": {
                    "url": "https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/G7APqyfJ6lyi4l28noZj/media/6989327a38f77a2717eb4653.jpg",
                    "width": 600,
                    "autoWidth": true
                  },
                  "alt": "Celebration at Cameron Estate",
                  "width": 520,
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "padding": "0 40px 30px 40px",
                  "borderRadius": 6
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#F5F1EB",
          "padding": "0 0 0 0"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "faq03",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "faqcol03",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head04",
                "values": {
                  "text": "\"What if we need to cancel or postpone?\"",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text04",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Life happens. People's circumstances change. Even the best-laid plans sometimes need to shift. We understand that, and our policies reflect that reality.</p><p>Here's how our deposit and payment structure works:</p><p><strong>Initial deposit</strong> — This holds your date on our calendar. It's non-refundable, as is standard in the industry (because when we hold your date, we turn away other couples who might want it).</p><p><strong>Payment schedule</strong> — Your remaining balance is spread out over the course of your engagement, making it manageable rather than one large payment.</p><p>I'm happy to walk through the specific terms with you — just ask. Transparency is important to us.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 10px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "faq04",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "faqcol04",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head05",
                "values": {
                  "text": "\"How do we actually know it's the right choice?\"",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text05",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Honestly? You won't know completely until your wedding day. That's the honest truth about planning a celebration this important — you're making decisions years in advance about something you can't fully experience until it happens.</p><p>But here's what couples tell us: they felt <strong>relief</strong>, not anxiety, when they made their decision. They felt ready to stop searching and start planning. They could picture their day here, and that picture felt right.</p><p>If you're feeling anxious or uncertain, keep exploring. If you're feeling relief and excitement when you think about Cameron Estate, that's worth paying attention to.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 10px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "faq05",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "faqcol05",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head06",
                "values": {
                  "text": "\"What happens next if we book?\"",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#D4AF37",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 22,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 10px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text06",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Here's what the rest of your wedding planning journey looks like with Cameron Estate:</p><p><strong>Step 1:</strong> You select your date and secure it with your deposit. The date is officially yours.</p><p><strong>Step 2:</strong> We schedule a comprehensive planning meeting — either in person or virtual, whatever works for you — to discuss your vision in detail. Colors, flowers, menu preferences, timeline, all of it.</p><p><strong>Step 3:</strong> You receive your dedicated coordinator — the person who will guide you through every step of the planning process, answer your questions, help you make decisions, and manage all the details.</p><p><strong>Step 4:</strong> We handle all vendor coordination. Your coordinator works with your florist, photographer, DJ, and any other vendors to make sure everyone is on the same page.</p><p><strong>Step 5:</strong> We manage timeline planning, setup, and day-of execution. You show up on your wedding day, and we handle everything.</p><p>That's the beauty of having one team manage everything: you get to actually enjoy your wedding day instead of managing it.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "values": {
          "backgroundColor": "#FFFFFF",
          "padding": "30px 40px 10px 40px"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "cta01",
        "columns": [
          {
            "id": "ctacol01",
            "width": 100,
            "contents": [
              {
                "type": "heading",
                "id": "head07",
                "values": {
                  "text": "Questions I Didn't Anticipate?",
                  "tag": "h2",
                  "color": "#2C3E50",
                  "fontFamily": "Cormorant Garamond",
                  "fontSize": 24,
                  "fontWeight": 500,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 15px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "id": "text07",
                "values": {
                  "text": "<p>Let's talk. I'm here to answer anything I haven't covered.</p><p>Or reach out however works best for you:</p><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:ceiweddings@cameronestateinn.com\" style=\"color: #2C3E50;\">ceiweddings@cameronestateinn.com</a><br/>Phone: 717-725-4831</p><p>Take your time. Good decisions aren't rushed — but our calendar is real, and availability does shift as couples make decisions. If you've been thinking about Cameron Estate, I hope you'll give us the chance to show you around.</p>",
                  "color": "#4A4A4A",
                  "fontFamily": "Poppins",
                  "fontSize": 16,
                  "lineHeight": 1.7,
                  "alignment": "left",
                  "padding": "0 0 25px 0"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "button",
                "id": "btn01",
                "values": {
